OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry
OL,6,Finitially this evening, but a band of
OL,7,Fwet and windy weather will sweep
OL,8,Facross the region overnight. Rain
OL,9,Fclearing east towards dawn allowing
OL,10,Fsome clearer spells to develop.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA brighter day tomorrow
OL,13,Fwith a mix of cloud and sunny spells.
OL,14,FThe odd light shower is possible but
OL,15,Fmost will be dry with winds easing.
OL,16,FTemperatures around average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
