OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FUnsettled and windy on Thursday with a
OL,7,Fband of heavy rain arriving later.
OL,8,FColder with some blustery showers on
OL,9,FFriday, before turning drier and less
OL,10,Fcold on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
